listitem.para:
[If you do not already have a project-based diagram open (see section 2.1 above -
              option 'Open Diagram')] From the File menu select
                New Diagram of Type and then Standard Diagram (database driven);

Select the two, or more, entities you need (SHIFT button held down); right click;
              choose the menu item Add relation, and then select
              the type of relation you want. The entities will be linked accordingly.
